New York has closed primaries (unless you're 1 of the few who can buy you're way in). Deadline: Received by Friday, October 9, 2015.

Resources to register and understand the voting/delegate process:

* https://voterlookup.elections.state.ny.us/votersearch.aspx
* http://dmv.ny.gov/org/more-info/electronic-voter-registration-application
* https://vote.usa.gov
* https://register2.rockthevote.com/registrants/new/?state=NY&partner=1&source=rtv.com-voterregdeadlines
* http://voteforbernie.org/#ny (also has deadline and registration info for other states for those wondering)